Package ohos.agp.components

Class CornerMark

  • java.lang.Object
    • ohos.agp.components.CornerMark

  • public class CornerMark
extends Object
    Represents a corner mark class to mark components.

    corner mark elements are added for components in a container to display a corner mark on top of a component.

    Since:
    5
